A 12-year-old boy died when an ox-drawn cart he was riding overturned and trapped him in Chivhu, Mashonaland province in Zimbabwe.The death of Never Haparari was confirmed by the Mashonaland East police on Monday.Never was riding with his brother Kudakwashe Haparari when the two ox pulling the cart suddenly started acting maniacal, police told newzimbabwe.com.Kudakwashe managed to disembark from the cart but when the cart approached a curve it overturned, trapping Never inside.Letwin Dandajena,50,who witnessed the accident attempted to assist but Never was already dead. He sustained deep cuts on his right ear and on his head, newzimbabwe.com reported.Sadza police are still investigating.-Tatenda Chiriseri